UID:Ad6vkdfgxugzpjhv8z6iF
SUMMARY:Latino Founders Forum - Lymbar Hosted
DTSTAMP:20260628T094103Z
DTSTART:20260630T170000Z
DESCRIPTION:Register here: https://luma.com/Latino-Founders-Forum \nThe Jun
	e edition of the Latino Founders Forum Houston is on June 30th ⚽🎉 \n​After
	 a strong launch that brought out 50+ founders\, operators\, investors\, c
	reatives\, and professionals\, the forum is keeping the momentum going wit
	h a special World Cup Celebration edition of our monthly gathering. \n​Yes
	\, it’s called Latino Founders Forum — but it’s not only for Latinos. Anyo
	ne is welcome to pull up\, grab a drink\, wear their favorite soccer jerse
	y\, make meaningful connections\, and be part of the community. \n​This is
	 a monthly event for people building real things in Houston. While the for
	um is rooted in supporting and elevating Latino founders\, the room is ope
	n to anyone who values entrepreneurship\, culture\, community\, and genuin
	e relationships. \nThey’re back at The Lymbar inside the Ion for another h
	igh-quality happy hour designed to bring together founders\, funders\, adv
	isors\, builders\, creatives\, and professionals who want to meet ambitiou
	s people in a room that actually feels worth being in. \n​This month\, the
	y’re bringing a World Cup vibe to the night and inviting guests to wear th
	eir favorite soccer jersey as we celebrate culture\, connection\, and comm
	unity in Houston. Expect a great atmosphere\, strong energy\, good drinks\
	, and the kind of conversations that make these events worth showing up fo
	r. \n​Come for the jerseys\, drinks\, and festive energy. Stay for the peo
	ple\, the conversations\, and the chance to be part of Houston’s growing s
	tartup and business community. \n​If you came to one of the earlier events
	\, you already know the energy. If you haven’t yet\, this is a great one t
	o start with. \n​Built by founders. Powered by community. Open to everyone
	.\n\nhttps://iondistrict.com/event/latino-founders-forum-lymbar-hosted/\n\
	nFrom Ion District
URL:https://iondistrict.com/event/latino-founders-forum-lymbar-hosted/
LOCATION:The Lymbar
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:ion-district
CATEGORIES:Ion District
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT3H
END:VEVENT
